      "csl:pageColumn": "3-0716",
      "rdf:value": "<L>34090<pc>3-0716<k1>dURASa<k2>dURA/Sa<h>1\n1. {#dURA/Sa#}¦ (2. {#duz + nASa#} {%Erreichung%}, {#duH'naSa#} <is>Padap</is>.)\n<ls>ṚV. PRĀT. 5,24.</ls>\n<ls>VS. PRĀT. 3,42.</ls>\n<ls>P. 6,3,109</ls>, <is>Vārtt</is>. 6. <lex>adj.</lex> <lex>f.</lex> {#A#} <ab>dass.</ab>: {#dU\\RASe\\yaM dakzi^RA pArTi\\vAnA^m#}\n<ls>ṚV. 6,27,8.</ls> {#(rayiM duzwaraM) yo dU\\RASo^ vanuzya\\tA#}\n<ls n=\"ṚV.\">9,63,11.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 2) <lex>m.</lex> <ab>N.</ab> eines <is>Ekāha</is>\n<ls>KĀTY. ŚR. 22,8,26.</ls>\n<ls>ŚĀṄKH. ŚR. 14,32,3</ls>, <ab>Schol.</ab> <ls>MAŚ.</ls> in <ls>Verz. d. B. H. 72 (IV,7)</ls>; <ab>s.</ab> 1. {#durASa#} .\n<div n=\"v\">— <ab>Vgl.</ab> {#durRaSa#} .\n<LEND>"
